  <Folder><name>Everest Base Camp (EBC) Trek</name>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Everest Base Camp (EBC) Trek</name>
      <description>Route: Lukla – Phakding – Namche Bazaar – Tengboche – Dingboche – Lobuche – Gorak Shep – Everest Base Camp
Rescue points: 7
Rescue altitude range: 2,860m to 5,364m</description>
      <styleUrl>#everest-base-camp-ebc-trek-line</styleUrl>
      <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>86.73139,27.68778,0 86.71256,27.74004,0 86.71058,27.80528,0 86.76394,27.835951,0 86.831444,27.892303,0 86.7908,27.9587,0 86.82856,27.98098,0 86.85324,28.00369,0</coordinates></LineString>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Lukla</name>
      <description>Route(s): Everest Base Camp (EBC) Trek; Gokyo Valley Trek (and Renjo La Pass)
Altitude: 2,860m
Notes: nearest airstrip and primary medevac point; Lukla Hospital is a short but arduous uphill walk from the landing area | Full heli services; primary evac point with airstrip
Approximate coordinate: No</description>
      <Point><coordinates>86.73139,27.68778,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Namche Bazaar</name>
      <description>Route(s): Everest Base Camp (EBC) Trek; Gokyo Valley Trek (and Renjo La Pass)
Altitude: 3,440m
Notes: major evacuation hub; has helipad on top of a hill | Major evacuation hub with helipad on top of a hill
Approximate coordinate: No</description>
      <Point><coordinates>86.71058,27.80528,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
